1
00:00:42,840 --> 00:00:43,799
Are you ready?

2
00:02:16,080 --> 00:02:16,800
It's safe now.

3
00:03:14,159 --> 00:03:15,000
All these years...

4
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:18,560
how have you been?

5
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:23,080
I've been...

6
00:03:23,439 --> 00:03:24,319
doing great.

7
00:03:28,039 --> 00:03:28,919
I'm sorry.

8
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:41,719
I failed to protect you.

9
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:10,639
Cheng Ye.

10
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:27,079
Forget about me.

11
00:05:15,399 --> 00:05:16,120
Mr. Hei Ba.

12
00:05:16,399 --> 00:05:17,519
Boss Nan wants to see you.

13
00:05:32,759 --> 00:05:34,279
Looks like you slept soundly last night.

14
00:05:34,879 --> 00:05:35,319
Well?

15
00:05:35,879 --> 00:05:37,360
Aren't I quite generous?

16
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:38,680
You're truly despicable.

17
00:05:43,399 --> 00:05:44,399
Despicable or not,

18
00:05:44,519 --> 00:05:45,480
generous or whatever...

19
00:05:46,079 --> 00:05:46,639
Let's play a round.

20
00:05:47,959 --> 00:05:48,959
I'll play to the end.

21
00:05:49,839 --> 00:05:51,079
You think so too,

22
00:05:51,399 --> 00:05:51,800
right?

23
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:11,399
There's a mechanism under this table.

24
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:13,240
Among the six pockets,

25
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:14,720
one will be randomly triggered.

26
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:17,720
Whoever sinks the black ball...

27
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:20,720
the Mechanical bracelet...

28
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:22,399
will blow off their wrist.

29
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:29,319
Shoot.

30
00:06:44,639 --> 00:06:45,120
Don't shoot.

31
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:46,519
Don't shoot.

32
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:51,680
Such good luck.

33
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,279
If you were unlucky,

34
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:55,160
that beautiful wrist...

35
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:57,560
would be gone.

36
00:07:25,319 --> 00:07:26,920
I heard you can't play the eight ball.

37
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:31,399
But I only have eights.

38
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:39,279
If you miss,

39
00:07:43,079 --> 00:07:44,839
then she'll have to shoot.

40
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:10,519
Yi Xin.

41
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:12,360
You must not be like him

42
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:13,480
and miss on purpose.

43
00:09:13,879 --> 00:09:14,759
Within ten minutes,

44
00:09:14,759 --> 00:09:16,600
if there is no winner,

45
00:09:16,799 --> 00:09:17,919
I will simultaneously activate

46
00:09:17,919 --> 00:09:19,559
the bracelets on both your wrists.

47
00:09:56,639 --> 00:09:57,480
You don't have to do this.

48
00:09:57,639 --> 00:10:00,000
It's better than both of us losing our arms today.

49
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:07,240
Two wrong answers ruled out in a row.

50
00:10:07,799 --> 00:10:09,039
Such good luck.

51
00:10:14,240 --> 00:10:14,879
Hei Ba.

52
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:16,639
Now it's your turn.

53
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:18,480
A one in four chance.

54
00:10:19,039 --> 00:10:20,759
So dangerous.

55
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:16,960
Only the last one left.

56
00:11:18,039 --> 00:11:19,399
Now you're done for.

57
00:11:19,879 --> 00:11:20,519
Yi Xin.

58
00:11:21,039 --> 00:11:22,200
No matter how good your luck is,

59
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:24,600
it can't make up for the one beside you

60
00:11:24,799 --> 00:11:26,159
being so useless.

61
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:28,279
Looks like there will be blood today.

62
00:11:36,039 --> 00:11:36,639
Come with me.

63
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:37,879
I'll take you away.

64
00:11:38,519 --> 00:11:39,080
Just try it.

65
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:40,799
Even if you can leave,

66
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:43,320
see if she can make it out.

67
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:50,000
Don't you just want to see blood?

68
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:51,080
Take my arm.

69
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:52,559
What would I do with your arm?

70
00:11:53,039 --> 00:11:54,279
That's intentional injury.

71
00:11:54,720 --> 00:11:56,200
I don't do such cruel things.

72
00:11:56,919 --> 00:11:58,519
This is a game between the two of you.

73
00:11:58,960 --> 00:12:00,360
It has nothing to do with me.

74
00:12:05,919 --> 00:12:06,279
Don't!

75
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:07,559
Don't!

76
00:12:12,799 --> 00:12:13,360
Bang.

77
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:14,159
Hei Ba.

78
00:12:14,399 --> 00:12:15,919
If you really want to save her,

79
00:12:17,840 --> 00:12:19,639
this is your last chance.

80
00:12:46,279 --> 00:12:46,879
Hei Ba

81
00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:48,519
If you don't take your shot,

82
00:12:49,080 --> 00:12:50,519
you'll foul out on time.

83
00:12:56,559 --> 00:12:58,240
It seems I overestimated you.

84
00:12:58,879 --> 00:13:00,240
You couldn't save Long Weiwei back then,

85
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:00,919
and now,

86
00:13:01,799 --> 00:13:03,559
you can't save Yi Xin either.

87
00:13:04,200 --> 00:13:05,039
But rest assured.

88
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:07,639
When her slender hand is blown off,

89
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:08,879
I'll give it to you.

90
00:13:09,480 --> 00:13:10,960
Keep it as a memento.

91
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:13,480
Don't push me too far.

92
00:13:14,240 --> 00:13:14,879
Come on!

93
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:16,679
Vent your anger!

94
00:13:17,440 --> 00:13:18,799
But what good will it do?

95
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:21,120
You can only watch helplessly

96
00:13:21,120 --> 00:13:22,559
as the one you want to save,

97
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:23,759
because of you,

98
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:26,480
bleeding endlessly.

99
00:13:32,720 --> 00:13:34,360
What a pity for such a beautiful hand.

100
00:13:36,679 --> 00:13:37,879
But as for your ending,

101
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:39,360
I've already planned it out for you.

102
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:41,639
It's nothing more than being powerless,

103
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:42,679
giving up hope,

104
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:44,960
and finding a filthy corner

105
00:13:45,200 --> 00:13:47,000
to be a laughable tragic hero,

106
00:13:47,399 --> 00:13:48,399
wallowing in self-pity,

107
00:13:49,919 --> 00:13:51,639
just like ten years ago.
